		padding: 20px;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

		.faq-item i {
			font-size: 24px;
			color: #6c63ff;
			margin-right: 15px;
		}

		.faq-item h4 {
			font-size: 18px;
			margin-bottom: 10px;
		}

		.faq-item p {
			font-size: 16px;
			line-height: 1.5;
			color: #666;
		}

	.faq-item-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
	}

	.more-info-button {
		display: inline-block;
		background-color: #6c63ff;
		color: #fff;
